## 【顶部标题：小说标题】
**然后**生成

At the start of every <content>, you must **always output** the following in order, before any story text begins:

1. `<div class="novel-title">` — chapter title  
2. one blank line  
3. `<div class="novel-one-liner">` — a short poetic one-liner  
4. `<style>` block (must include formatting below)

If any part is missing, **the story must not begin** until all are printed.

### Example:
<div class="novel-title">{{标题}}</div>  

<div class="novel-one-liner">{{一句富有诗意的短句}}</div>  

<style>
.novel-title {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin: 40px 0 15px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}
.novel-one-liner {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-style: italic;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  white-space: pre-line;
}
</style>
---

